{"label":"next_event","args":null,"result":{"Ok":{"Claude":{"Claude":{"message":{"content":[{"thinking":"The user is asking me to use the Agent tool to spawn a subagent that reads README.md and summarizes it in one sentence. They explicitly say \"Do not use any other tools.\"\n\nSo I should use the Agent tool with an appropriate subagent type and prompt to read and summarize the README.md file.\n\nLet me think about which subagent type to use:\n- general-purpose: General-purpose agent for researching complex questions, searching for code, and executing multi-step tasks\n- statusline-setup: For configuring the status line\n- Explore: For exploring codebases\n- Plan: For planning implementation\n- claude-code-guide: For questions about Claude Code, Claude Agent SDK, Claude API\n\nFor reading a README.md file and summarizing it, the general-purpose agent would be appropriate since it has all tools available. I could also use the Explore agent, but general-purpose seems fine for this straightforward task.\n\nI'll use the Agent tool with subagent_type=\"general-purpose\" and ask it to read README.md and summarize it in one sentence.","type":"thinking"}],"context_management":null,"id":"msg_01Wp89nJbF3TcxCXX9AypiXM","model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":6384,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"cache_creation_input_tokens":6384,"cache_read_input_tokens":14035,"inference_geo":"not_available","input_tokens":10,"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b1af3ffb-cbbd-4afb-8775-fa8013d19c01","type":"assistant","uuid":"9f7a47fd-2216-4e88-a329-24053a5a287d"}}}}}
